    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-80ef-8573-d78119f90439",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Method for learning group composition that creates teams with different backgrounds using PSO. The algorithm is integrated into an e-learning system that needs to make an assignment of new members to team. The authors propose the following heuristic: maximize whithin group diversity and minimize between group diversity. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
